can be leveraged in an Agile new product

18
00:00:47.090 --> 00:00:49.090
development environment and how to make change

19
00:00:49.090 --> 00:00:53.010
a bit less painful along the way.

20
00:00:53.010 --> 00:00:55.040
If we continue exploring this concept

21
00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:58.020
of why change is painful, we can even trace

22
00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:00.060
some of the roots back to the education

