00:01:08.070 --> 00:01:12.060
leading texts say that by controlling change,

27
00:01:12.060 --> 00:01:15.050
you control cost, so it is a vital organ

28
00:01:15.050 --> 00:01:18.040
of the business and should be run efficiently.

29
00:01:18.040 --> 00:01:21.020
One can see from this quote how change

30
00:01:21.020 --> 00:01:24.060
is being positioned and used not only

31
00:01:24.060 --> 00:01:26.060
as a restrictive measure for engineering,

