says that the leading text describes

36
00:01:38.090 --> 00:01:42.080
the reason for change is for controlling

37
00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:45.000
design changes is to restrict

38
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.010
the otherwise limitless creativity of designers

