00:01:56.020 --> 00:02:01.030
as opposed to an Agile-mindset-like opportunity

44
00:02:01.030 --> 00:02:05.080
to involve customers, to define customer requirements,

45
00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:08.080
and to create greater customer satisfaction.

46
00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:12.070
So we need to look at how we can reposition change

47
00:02:12.070 --> 00:02:15.060
in the Agile mindset, but there's slightly more

48
00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:18.030
that we need to consider first.

