00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.010
that have very specific requirements around change.

52
00:02:28.010 --> 00:02:33.040
For example, if we were to look at the ISO 13485 documents

53
00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:37.060
which describe the new product development processes

