00:02:46.010 --> 00:02:47.090
that describes similar processes

57
00:02:47.090 --> 00:02:50.010
in the automotive supply chain industry,

58
00:02:50.010 --> 00:02:53.030
we would find a lot of commonalities.

59
00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:56.080
Some of the commonalities and some of the major findings

60
00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:59.080
related to change is that the standards require

