66
00:03:14.060 --> 00:03:18.070
Similarly, the standards require that all design changes

67
00:03:18.070 --> 00:03:21.070
are to be reviewed and approved by authorized personnel

68
00:03:21.070 --> 00:03:23.070
before their implementation.

69
00:03:23.070 --> 00:03:27.030
Again, this is out of alignment with the Agile mindset

70
00:03:27.030 --> 00:03:29.040
of making changes and making improvements

71
00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:34.030
as you go along so that the product evolves very rapidly.

72
00:03:34.030 --> 00:03:36.060
And lastly about International Standards,

73
00:03:36.060 --> 00:03:40.030
The International Standards prescribes some other

