00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:06.080
We have problem reports and change requests,

83
00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:09.010
and many of the artifacts that you're familiar with

84
00:04:09.010 --> 00:04:11.060
from the new product development process.

85
00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:14.020
Again, this is a lot of documentation

86
00:04:14.020 --> 00:04:15.070
that is out of alignment with the way

87
00:04:15.070 --> 00:04:18.060
Agile would prescribe change to be handled.

